<section class="questions-section">
  <Questions />
</section>

<section class="second-testimonial-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="blue-container">
      <div class="left-content">
        <div class="left-quote">
          <svg
            width="50"
            height="50"
            viewBox="0 0 8 8"
            fill="currentColor"
            color="#0273e7"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              d="M3 0c-1.65 0-3 1.35-3 3v3h3v-3h-2c0-1.11.89-2 2-2v-1zm5 0c-1.65 0-3 1.35-3 3v3h3v-3h-2c0-1.11.89-2 2-2v-1z"
              transform="translate(0 1)"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="left-title">
          <h4>
            Kadence is incredibly versatile, It’s really easy to build any type
            of website you can imagine.
          </h4>
        </div>

        <div class="left-stars">
          <p>★★★★★</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="right-content">
        <div class="right-photo">
          <img
            src="https://www.kadencewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/shawn-hekseth-wp101.jpeg"
            style="border-radius: 50%;"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="right-name">
          <p>Shawn Hesketh – WP101</p>
        </div>

        <div class="right-text">
          <em
            >At WP101, we recommend Kadence because it is highly <br /> optimized
            for performance and easy to customize.</em
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="gris">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="gris-header">
      <span class="gris-badge">Dato Curioso</span>
      <h2 class="gris-title">Los mejores del mundo también se protegen</h2>
      <p class="gris-subtitle">
        Cuando algo es verdaderamente valioso, protegerlo no es un lujo — es una
        decisión inteligente.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="facts-grid">
      <div class="fact-card">
        <div class="fact-quote">
          <svg
            width="32"
            height="32"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <path
              d="M10 8.5C10 5.46 7.54 3 4.5 3H3v2h1.5C6.43 5 8 6.57 8 8.5V9H3v6h6V9h1V8.5zM21 8.5C21 5.46 18.54 3 15.5 3H14v2h1.5C17.43 5 19 6.57 19 8.5V9h-5v6h6V9h1V8.5z"
              fill="#0273e7"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="fact-text">
          <strong>Cristiano Ronaldo</strong> aseguró sus piernas por más de <strong
            >100 millones de euros</strong
          >. Para él, proteger su mayor herramienta de trabajo no fue vanidad —
          fue visión.
        </p>
        <p class="fact-reflection">
          Porque cuando algo es valioso, lo proteges.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fact-card">
        <div class="fact-quote">
          <svg
            width="32"
            height="32"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <path
              d="M10 8.5C10 5.46 7.54 3 4.5 3H3v2h1.5C6.43 5 8 6.57 8 8.5V9H3v6h6V9h1V8.5zM21 8.5C21 5.46 18.54 3 15.5 3H14v2h1.5C17.43 5 19 6.57 19 8.5V9h-5v6h6V9h1V8.5z"
              fill="#0273e7"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="fact-text">
          <strong>Lionel Messi</strong> cuenta con una de las pólizas de seguro más
          altas en la historia del deporte, cubriendo lesiones que podrían terminar
          con su carrera. <strong>Prevenir es parte de ganar.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="fact-reflection">La mejor jugada siempre es anticiparse.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="fact-card">
        <div class="fact-quote">
          <svg
            width="32"
            height="32"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          >
            <path
              d="M10 8.5C10 5.46 7.54 3 4.5 3H3v2h1.5C6.43 5 8 6.57 8 8.5V9H3v6h6V9h1V8.5zM21 8.5C21 5.46 18.54 3 15.5 3H14v2h1.5C17.43 5 19 6.57 19 8.5V9h-5v6h6V9h1V8.5z"
              fill="#0273e7"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="fact-text">
          <strong>David Beckham</strong> aseguró todo su cuerpo por más de <strong
            >100 millones de dólares</strong
          > durante su carrera. Su imagen y su físico eran su patrimonio — y lo trató
          como tal.
        </p>
        <p class="fact-reflection">
          Tu patrimonio también merece esa protección.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="gris-closing">
      <p>No necesitas ser famoso para proteger lo que más importa.</p>
      <a href="/cotiza" class="gris-cta">Quiero proteger lo mío →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="carousel-section">
  <Carousel />
</section>

<section class="whatsapp-section">
  <Whatsapp />
</section>

<!-- <section class="help-section"> -->
<!--   <Help /> -->
<!-- </section> -->

<Footer />

<style>
  .carousel-section {
    margin: 0;
    /* height: 440px; */
  }

  .stars {
    color: #fab200;
    font-size: 40px;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
  }

  /* ===== GRIS / FACTS SECTION ===== */
  .gris {
    background-color: #f7f8fb;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 100px 0;
  }

  .gris-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 750px;
    margin: 0 auto 60px auto;
  }

  .gris-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #e8f0fe;
    color: #0273e7;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    padding: 6px 18px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .gris-title {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1c2d43;
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .gris-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #4b5563;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .facts-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 30px;
    max-width: 1350px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .fact-card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 36px 30px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    transition:
      transform 0.3s ease,
      box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .fact-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(2, 115, 231, 0.1);
  }

  .fact-quote {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .fact-text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #374151;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }

  .fact-text strong {
    color: #1c2d43;
  }

  .fact-reflection {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #0273e7;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .gris-closing {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 60px;
  }

  .gris-closing p {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: #1c2d43;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 24px 0;
  }

  .gris-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #0273e7;
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition:
      background 0.25s ease,
      transform 0.25s ease;
  }

  .gris-cta:hover {
    background: #0260c4;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .facts-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 550px;
    }

    .gris-title {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }
  }

  /* ===== FEATURES / QUIÉNES SOMOS ===== */
  .features {
    padding: 120px 0;
    background: #f8f9fc;
  }

  .features-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: auto;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .features-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #e8f0fe;
    color: #0273e7;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    padding: 6px 18px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .features-header h2 {
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1c2d43;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .features-header p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #1c2d43de;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .features-card {
    max-width: 1350px;
    margin: auto;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 40px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .features-images {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .features-images img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 14px;
  }

  .feature {
    display: flex;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    transition:
      background 0.25s ease,
      box-shadow 0.25s ease;
  }

  .feature:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .feature:hover {
    background: #f0f5ff;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(2, 115, 231, 0.08);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    background: #e8f0fe;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .feature-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .feature-content h3 {
    font-size: 22px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: #1c2d43;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .feature-role {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #0273e7;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .feature-content p {
    color: #1c2d43de;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 15px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 250px 1fr;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .testimonial-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  .testimonial-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .testimonial-text {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #374151;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 0;
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .author h4 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111827;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .author span {
    font-size: 12px;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    color: #6b7280;
  }

  .testimonial-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background-color: #f8f9fc;
    padding-bottom: 7rem;
  }

  .comilla-1 {
    width: 10%;
  }
  .comilla-2 {
    width: 70%;
  }
  .comilla-3 {
    display: flex;
    width: 10%;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }

  /* --- SLIDER STYLES --- */
  .container {
    max-width: 1350px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cards-slider-section {
    background: #eeeff7;
    padding: 120px 0;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  .header-with-arrows {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .header-text h3 {
    font-size: 2.7rem;
    width: 70%;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1c2d43;
    margin: 0 0 10px 0;
  }

  .slider-arrows {
    display: flex;
    gap: 15px;
  }

  .arrow {
    cursor: pointer;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
    padding: 10px;
  }

  .arrow.left {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .slider {
    display: flex;
    gap: 30px;
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scrollbar-width: none;
    padding-left: calc((100vw - 1370px) / 2);
    padding-right: 40px;
  }

  .slider::-webkit-scrollbar {
    display: none;
